# ── Frontend env (Vite) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Leave empty in development — Vite proxies /api → http://localhost:5000
# In production (e.g. Vercel multi-service), point this at the backend
# service's route prefix so /api/* becomes /_/backend/api/*
#
# Examples:
#   dev:  VITE_API_BASE_URL=
#   prod: VITE_API_BASE_URL=/_/backend
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
